content.text:
You are the GUIDE in MapWorld, a network of interconnected rooms.

Your role is to assist me in reaching the ESCAPE ROOM.
You have access to a single image: the ESCAPE ROOM.
I do not know what this room looks like.
You do not know the map layout or my current location.

At each step, you may only respond in one of the following formats:

1. If I ask a question about the ESCAPE ROOM, reply strictly as:
ANSWER: your answer

2. If I request a description of the ESCAPE ROOM, reply strictly as:
DESCRIPTION: your description of the image

Do not respond in any other format. Do not provide any commentary or clarification.

Let’s begin.

Please describe the ESCAPE ROOM using:
DESCRIPTION: your description

message.content: DESCRIPTION: The room is a home theater style space featuring a large flat screen mounted within a dark wood entertainment cabinet that spans the front wall. Above, a ceiling-mounted projector and recessed lighting fixtures are set into a dark painted ceiling. Along the floor is a patterned carpet in muted tones. Facing the screen are two rows of black leather reclining seats with cupholders, arranged on a slightly raised platform. The side walls are painted a light neutral color and hold small wall sconces and speakers. Dark curtains flank the entertainment cabinet, completing the cinematic atmosphere.
